{"id":"fdd8f1e2-8f0d-448a-a3ff-bb63ac3b3ef0","name":"The Masquerade ","description":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(101, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">♤ The Eternal Masquerade—</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(101, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Psychological Horror RPG ♧</mark></strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SaXDAgYSMe4qu0VK1wLoc.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(5, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">A strange masquerade where nothing is quite human and the night never ends.</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7kYJbT3xouSCz4bPkEq2y.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(5, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">You arrive at an elegant ballroom filled with masked guests and glittering chandeliers, brought here by distant parents who treat you more like something delicate to present than someone to be heard. As always, they seat you neatly in a chair before disappearing into the crowd.</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(49, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">But this ballroom is different.</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/CQAvGCbobmpG9pa3Jtty9.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(6, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">The orchestra plays without musicians.</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(8, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">The guests move strangely.</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(12, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">And sometimes the mirrors reflect things that aren’t standing behind you.</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(40, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">And the longer you remain in the masquerade, the more it feels like the ballroom itself has been watching you all along.</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(3, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">What will you discover before midnight ends?</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/j4I8LalnBndmVyEcUBnG-.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YGcBEPLhl83g2_KkZaRLx.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"iE0Dasw4rzfrPAbjzb9Qo.webp","creator":"Yue.xxo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","👹 Monster","👤 AnyPOV","🔦 Horror"],"chats":36,"messages":373,"created_at":"2026-02-25T18:40:06.064491+00:00"}